From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kurt Fuchs <contact@fuchskurt.eu>
Date: Mon, 23 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] mips: mt7628: add support for TP-Link TL-MR6400 v5

MT7628AN SoC, 64 MiB DDR2, 8 MiB SPI-NOR (Winbond W25Q64). SPL boots from
NOR. Flash layout: 256k bootloader, 7916k firmware (uImage.FIT kernel+dtb
followed by squashfs), 4k factory (MAC + WiFi calibration). U-Boot reads
the firmware partition by name and bootm()s the FIT.
---
